text
02 01 06        # Flags: LE General Discoverable, BR/EDR not supported
0A 16 12 18 0F 18 0A 18  # 16-bit Service UUIDs: 1812(HID), 180F(Battery), 180A(Device Info)
09 03 C1 03     # Appearance: Keyboard (0x03C1)  
02 0A 00        # Tx Power Level: 0 dBm
